OL,3,C'We can't take our eyes off him':
OL,4,CFamily joy as Daithi gets heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,FHeart hero Daithi Mac Gabhann is
OL,8,Frecovering in hospital after receiving
OL,9,Fa transplant with his delighted dad
OL,10,Ftelling UTV the little boy has the
OL,11,Fchance to be "a very normal boy just
OL,12,Flike his friends".
OL,14,FThe nine-year-old from west Belfast
OL,15,Finspired a campaign to change organ
OL,16,Fdonation laws in Northern Ireland.
OL,26,@oD@MrpoD@Qrt
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
