CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784661517
OL,3,C'We can't take our eyes off him':
OL,4,CFamily joy as Daithi gets heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,FHe was born with the rare hypoplastic
OL,8,Fleft heart syndrome and had been on
OL,9,Fthe waiting list for a heart
OL,10,Ftransplant since 2018 - thought to be
OL,11,Fthe longest of any child in the world.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784661517
OL,3,C'We can't take our eyes off him':
OL,4,CFamily joy as Daithi gets heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,FHis parents Mairtin and Steph
OL,8,Fcampaigned for years for a move
OL,9,Ftowards a soft opt-out law and to
OL,10,Fpromote organ donation. But in June
OL,11,F2023 Daithi's Law came into effect,
OL,12,Fbringing Northern Ireland in line with
OL,13,Fthe rest of the UK. The Organ and
OL,14,FTissue Donation (Deemed Consent)
OL,15,Flegislation changed the way consent is
OL,16,Fgranted.
OL,18,FAdults are now deemed to have given
OL,19,Fconsent as a potential organ donor
OL,20,Fafter their death unless they choose
OL,21,Fto opt out or are in an excluded group.
OL,26,@sD@GrpsD@Krt
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784661517
OL,3,C'We can't take our eyes off him':
OL,4,CFamily joy as Daithi gets heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,FAnd after revealing how little Daithi
OL,8,Fhad at last been given "the gift" of a
OL,9,Fnew heart at Newcastle's Freeman
OL,10,FHospital, Mairtin said: "Thankfully,
OL,11,Fthe transplant itself has gone well,
OL,12,Fand Daithi has done well to come out
OL,13,Fof the procedure.
OL,15,F"He has a new heart beating inside him
OL,16,Fand it's doing the work. And he's
OL,17,Fdoing really well so far.
OL,26,@oD@arpoD@erttD@FrptD@Jrt
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784661517
OL,3,C'We can't take our eyes off him':
OL,4,CFamily joy as Daithi gets heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,F"Now, every time I allow myself to
OL,8,Fhave a wee smile or to think of the
OL,9,Funbelievable memories we can create in
OL,10,Fthe future, I remind myself that we're
OL,11,Fat the very early stages of the
OL,12,Fjourney. But at this moment in time,
OL,13,Fwe're hearing words like 'progress',
OL,14,Fwe're hearing words like 'he's doing
OL,15,Fwell', so, at this early stage in his
OL,16,Frecovery, he is doing really well.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784661517
OL,3,C'We can't take our eyes off him':
OL,4,CFamily joy as Daithi gets heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,F"But we're at a critical stage, and he
OL,8,Fdid have a biopsy yesterday to check
OL,9,Ffor rejection, which we're still
OL,10,Fwaiting on the results of. So,
OL,11,Falthough, you know, he's, he is doing
OL,12,Fwell, we are still very cautious. It's
OL,13,Fthe call I've been waiting for, and
OL,14,Fthe whole family's been waiting for,
OL,15,Ffor so long, it's the call Daithi's
OL,16,Fbeen waiting for, and it still hasn't
OL,17,Fsunk in that that call has come."
OL,26,@wD@]rpwD@art
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784661517
OL,3,C'We can't take our eyes off him':
OL,4,CFamily joy as Daithi gets heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,FMairtin was made an MBE in 2024 and
OL,8,FDaithi was awarded the freedom of
OL,9,FBelfast in 2023 for their campaigning
OL,10,Fwork.
OL,12,FAnd the delighted dad said he wouldn't
OL,13,Fstop fighting to raise awareness about
OL,14,Forgan donation.
OL,16,FHe added: "If people thought I was bad
OL,17,Ftalking about organ donation before
OL,18,Fthen this will hopefully only be the
OL,19,Fstart - because the change that we've
OL,20,Fseen already, people need to see this.
OL,26,@pD@BrppD@Frt
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784661517
OL,3,C'We can't take our eyes off him':
OL,4,CFamily joy as Daithi gets heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,F"And this gift has come about from
OL,8,Fpeople knowing about organ donation,
OL,9,Fpeople talking about organ donation,
OL,10,Fand people having that generosity in
OL,11,Ftheir hearts to say yes to organ
OL,12,Fdonation.
OL,14,F"And, to me, that all comes from
OL,15,Fpeople being aware and people knowing.
OL,16,FSo, the campaign won't stop. It'll
OL,17,Fprobably take a pivot in some way, but
OL,18,Fwe will keep talking about how
OL,19,Fprecious organ donation and that gift
OL,20,Fof life is."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784661517
OL,3,C'We can't take our eyes off him':
OL,4,CFamily joy as Daithi gets heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,FMairtin said he and Steph were looking
OL,8,Fforward to simple things that other
OL,9,Fparents might take for granted.
OL,11,FHe explained: "If the recovery goes as
OL,12,Fplanned, and, and Daithi keeps meeting
OL,13,Fthese milestones that he's already
OL,14,Fmade, that, you know, his life will be
OL,15,Ftransformed, that there may be a time
OL,16,Fwhere he won't need a wheelchair,
OL,17,Fwhere he won't need oxygen.
OL,26,@tD@TrptD@Xrt
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784661517
OL,3,C'We can't take our eyes off him':
OL,4,CFamily joy as Daithi gets heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,F"His lips are pink. His lips are pink
OL,8,Fat the minute. He doesn't have blue
OL,9,Flips anymore. He doesn't have blue
OL,10,Ffingers or blue toes. His saturation
OL,11,Flevels are, are really good, and even
OL,12,Fjust seeing that transformation
OL,13,Falready at this very early stage...I'm
OL,14,Fjust looking at him and I'm trying not
OL,15,Fto pinch his wee red cheeks.
OL,17,F"One of the, the biggest things that
OL,18,Fwe can see in his face already are his
OL,19,Fbeautiful freckles. And people might
OL,20,Fbe thinking, 'Why is he talking about
OL,21,Fhis freckles?'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784661517
OL,3,C'We can't take our eyes off him':
OL,4,CFamily joy as Daithi gets heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,F"It's because these are things that we
OL,8,Fhaven't seen in Daithi before, him
OL,9,Fhaving pink lips and, and warm hands
OL,10,Fand warm feet, those, those little
OL,11,Fthings that people probably take for
OL,12,Fgranted, and we're just blown away by
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,F"But we're hoping, as he gets
OL,16,Fstronger, he'll be able to walk by
OL,17,Fhimself, run by himself, maybe even
OL,18,Fplay some football. He wants me to go
OL,19,Fto Sports Direct and get boxing gloves
OL,20,Fand boxing pads to help with his
OL,21,Fphysio.
OL,26,@pD@RrppD@Vrt
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784661517
OL,3,C'We can't take our eyes off him':
OL,4,CFamily joy as Daithi gets heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,F"These are things that he's talking
OL,8,Fabout already. So, at this very early
OL,9,Fstage, um, if things keep going the
OL,10,Fway that we hope that they go, you
OL,11,Fknow, we can have a very normal boy,
OL,12,Fand that's all he's ever wanted to be,
OL,13,Fjust like his friends in school.
OL,15,F" I can't take my eyes off him, to be
OL,16,Fhonest. And I know his mum can't take
OL,17,Fher eyes off him, either.
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/13
